    "description": "<strong><i>You play as &quot;You&quot; an antisocial student who transferred to a new school. But this time, &quot;You&quot; decide to turn things around and decide to be more social: Make friends, and hopefully a Girlfriend.</i></strong><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1807740/extras/13ba1985824afea940c8fcb45524f91f.avif?t=1725082782\" width=616 height=200 /></span><br><br>Explore your new school and your new town, Interact with your friends and your love interest, spend time with them and get to know about them more.<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1807740/extras/bbd90e6e1082bfdc05c55705df946dcb.avif?t=1725082782\" width=616 height=200 /></span><br><br>Pick your love interest, Reach for the feelings of your loved one. Choose one of the three female protagonists to be your beloved.<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1807740/extras/07f45372621933fb5e34a8fd898712e2.avif?t=1725082782\" width=616 height=200 /></span><br><br>Or, spend some time with your new best friends instead.<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1807740/extras/c2032494a71190ace54e641872c620fa.avif?t=1725082782\" width=616 height=200 /></span><br><br>Explore all the possibilities, this game has 5 endings, the choices matter in this game and the choice is yours.<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1807740/extras/bc9dec33422fad0c23458156f77c5132.avif?t=1725082782\" width=616 height=200 /></span><br><br>Enjoy the colourful and beautiful artwork in Full HD 1080 Resolution.",
